import React from 'react'
import {Row} from 'react-bootstrap'
import CardMovie from './CardMovie'

const MoviesList = ({movies}) => {
  return (
      <Row className='mt-3'>
        movies.
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
        <CardMovie />
      </Row>
  )
}

export default MoviesList
